name: Saint Nobody
description:
Among my friends there are extraordinary people ... These are the people of the Giants, the Heroes of our time.

One of these Giants is Nikolai Poplavsky, a master of sound, a fiery spirit of creativity, young Krishna. I feel light, goodness and millions of tons of joy in him.
If he could be cloned, then he could easily play the role of all 33 heroes from Pushkin's fairy tale.)

Neo Heroes series, 2021
